snippet.title: Are Companies Cheating Us? | Dreamz Unlimited | Consumer Protection
snippet.description:
How Can a Customer Fight for Their Rights?
Every customer has the right to safety, information, choice, and redressal. But what can you do when these rights are violated? Here's how a customer can fight for their rights:
Know Your Rights - First, be aware of your basic consumer rights ‚Äî such as the right to be informed, the right to choose, the right to safety, and the right to seek redressal.
Keep Proof - Always keep receipts, bills, warranty cards, emails, or any communication related to the product or service. These documents act as evidence if a complaint needs to be raised.
Talk to the Seller - In many cases, simply raising the issue with the shop or service provider politely can solve the problem.
File a Formal Complaint - If the seller refuses to help, you can file a complaint with: Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
(Respective States)
Use Social Media - Tagging companies on social platforms like Twitter or Instagram often gets their attention quickly. Many companies take online reputation seriously.
Take Legal Action - If needed, you can approach a consumer court. These courts are specially set up to handle consumer disputes in a quicker and more affordable manner.
This video is produced by
Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection

localized.title: Are Companies Cheating Us? | Dreamz Unlimited | Consumer Protection
localized.description:
How Can a Customer Fight for Their Rights?
Every customer has the right to safety, information, choice, and redressal. But what can you do when these rights are violated? Here's how a customer can fight for their rights:
Know Your Rights - First, be aware of your basic consumer rights ‚Äî such as the right to be informed, the right to choose, the right to safety, and the right to seek redressal.
Keep Proof - Always keep receipts, bills, warranty cards, emails, or any communication related to the product or service. These documents act as evidence if a complaint needs to be raised.
Talk to the Seller - In many cases, simply raising the issue with the shop or service provider politely can solve the problem.
File a Formal Complaint - If the seller refuses to help, you can file a complaint with: Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
(Respective States)
Use Social Media - Tagging companies on social platforms like Twitter or Instagram often gets their attention quickly. Many companies take online reputation seriously.
Take Legal Action - If needed, you can approach a consumer court. These courts are specially set up to handle consumer disputes in a quicker and more affordable manner.
This video is produced by
Department of Legal Metrology & Consumer Protection
Govt. of Nagaland

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

snippet.description:
Kalyana Veetu Rasam
Ready to unlock the secret to that irresistible wedding rasam? Chef Deena is on a mission, and he's teamed up with Chennai's very own young culinary whiz, Mr. Harish from Janani Catering Services in West Mambalam!  Get ready to learn the nuances of an aromatic and flavorful rasam recipe, a staple at South Indian weddings, as Mr. Harsh guides us through the step-by-step process. Let's dive in and discover the magic of Janani Catering's Kalyanam Rasam! 

Sri Janani Catering Service
Mr. Harish
Contact : 9840703703

‡Æï‡Æ≤‡Øç‡ÆØ‡Ææ‡Æ£ ‡Æµ‡ØÄ‡Æü‡Øç‡Æü‡ØÅ ‡Æ∞‡Æö‡ÆÆ‡Øç | Kalyaana Veettu Rasam (Wedding-Style Rasam)
Thakkali Rasam
Tomato - 1 Kg
Mustard - 1 Tsp
Cumin Seeds - 1 Tsp
Pepper - 35 g
Asafoetida - 1 Tsp
Tamarind - 100 g
Jaggerry - 1/2 Tsp
Chrushed Garlic - 100 g
Dry Red Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos 
Green Chilli - 6 to 7 Nos
Curry Leaves - As Required 
Coriander Leaves - As Required 
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 Tsp
Salt - To Taste 
Gingelly Oil - 200 ml 
Ghee - For Tempering
 


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

snippet.title: He wasn‚Äôt just a man, he was a MONSTER | 3 years for KGF2 | Yash | Prashanth Neel | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
Celebrating 3 years of KGF Chapter 2 ‚Äì the film that redefined mass cinema and gave us the unstoppable Monster, Rocky Bhai

Written and Directed by Prashanth Neel
Produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the Banner "Hombale Films".
Starring: Rocking Star Yash, Sanjay Dutt, Srinidhi Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Prakash Raj, Malvika Avinash, Achyuth Kumar, Ayyappa P. Sharma, Rao Ramesh, Eshwari Rao, Archana Jois, T. S. Nagabharana, Saran, Avinash, Lakki Lakshman, Vashishta Simha, Harish Rai, Dinesh Mangalore, Tarak, Ramachandra Raju, Vinay Bidappa, Ashok Sharma, Mohan Juneja, Govinda Gowda, John Kokken, Srinivas Murthy.

Director of Photography: Bhuvan Gowda
Sound Design, Music & Background Score: Ravi Basrur
Co-director : Kirtan Nadagouda & Dhool Prakash
Direction Team: Bhargav N, Prashanth Hosmane, Chandan Bhargav, Yuvindraja, Nishanth Varma,  Muruli Muddenahally,Sanjay, Ghattimutthu Shashidhar, Abhijith Gorachi, Shiva Kumar, Mithilesh Gowda, Akash Thaargar, Akash Rambo, Roshan Sharif Farman Ullah.
Cameraman Team: Sandy, Prajwal Gowda, Kumar Gowda, Sagar Gowda, Manuraj  
Still - M G Narayan(Nani)
Executive Producer: K. V Rama Rao
Editor: Ujwal Kulkarni
Production Design: Shivakumar
Action: Anbariv
Choreography: Harsha, Mohan
Dubbing: Anand Y. S
Costume Designer: Yogi G Raj, Sania Sardhariya, Navin Shetty, Ashwin Mawle, Hassan Khan
Dialogues: Chandramouli.M, Dr. Suri, Prashanth Neel
Sound Effects: Nanndhu J & Team
Production Managers: K S Champakadama,Gagan Murthy, S Kumar
Production Incharge: Chidanand, Suresh Shankarananhalli, Shashikanth
DI & VFX: Unify Media
VFX Supervisor: Konda Reddy Suresh
Colorist: Fergus Hally, Ashwath
Marketing: Likitha Reddy, Naren Marol, Anil Kumar, Shreya Unchalli, Suman, Sunith shetty, Adith, Sai pavan
PRO: Sudheendra Venkatesh (Kannada), Vamsi Kaka (Telugu), Yuvraaj (Tamil), Vivek Ramadevan (Malayalam)
Digital Media PR: Prasad Bhimanadham
Art associate: Venkata Chalapathi, Kiran Kumar

snippet.title: Adventure | Stand-up Comedy by Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
When life gives you lemons, sell them and go to the mountains.
You‚Äôll come back with beautiful memories and a sore body.

This is a story about a trek I did with my friend.
I spend a lot of time in the mountains. There‚Äôs no place more peaceful.
But the moment I have to walk on uneven ground, everything changes. My body starts questioning my soul.
It‚Äôs tough, annoying, and sometimes painful.
But once I‚Äôm back home, all that‚Äôs left is a funny story‚Äîand now, that story will stay with all of us forever.

Hope you enjoyed the video.
Please like, comment & share it.

I‚Äôm also performing my stand-up comedy special in the UK and touring across India and internationally!
Tickets for all my shows are live here: https://linktr.ee/Shudhdesicomic

snippet.description:
A melody that will make your heart say, "Khudaya, Ishq, ho gaya." 
This one's all about #BringingLoveBack ‚ù§Ô∏è

Credits:
Song Name - Khudaya Ishq
Composer - Amit Trivedi

Lyrics - Kumaar
Music Producers - Amit Trivedi and Himonshu Parikh

A Richer Lens and Indian Stories Production Presents Abir Gulaal
#bringingloveback

Starring Fawad Khan, Vaani Kapoor, Lisa Haydon, Riddhi Dogra, Farida Jalal, Soni Razdan, Parmeet Sethi, Rahul Vora, Amrit Sandhu, Sujoy De, Zorawar Singh Ahluwalia and Dev Agrawal 
Directed by Aarti S Bagdi 
Produced by Vivek B. Agrawal, Avantika Hari, Rakesh Sippy, Firuzi Khan
Co-Producer - Raza Namazi

Choreographer - Vijay Ganguly
(London) Choreography - Rohan Shah & Shruti Shah
Cinematographer - Tribhuvan Babu Sadineni
Production Designer - Sunil Nigvekar

Lyrics:

Mukhda:
Lakh sitaron ki ek thi dua
Dil pe tabhi to zor na chala

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Main to loon sab saansein ab tere naam ki
Ik tu hi bas mera dunia kis kaam ki

Chadhe hain tere rang
Ke ab tere sang
Ye laage mann mera jogiya
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya..

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Antara:
Tere meri ishq kahani
Jaise dariya ka behta paani

Samjhega na koi
Hai ye baat ruhaani

Mere dil ke lafz churake
Kehti hai nazar deewani

Ik tu naya naya sa
Aur dunia lage puraani

Saari taarikhon pe haq hai tera
Aur kya chahun tu hai mera

Khudaya ishq re ishq re ishq re
Khudaya ishq hote hote ho gaya

Main to loon sab saansein ab tere naam ki

Chadhe hain tere rang

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Prepare to be captivated as Odisha's legendary actress, Aparajita Mohanty, steps into the enigmatic role of Ratnamala. The nightmare is just beginning...‚Äã

Babushaan Films and Sidharth Music proudly present Showcase 2 of Bou Buttu Bhuta, featuring the dynamic trio: Superstar Babushaan, Archita Sahu, and Aparajita Mohanty, and directed by Jagdish Mishra.

Mark your calendars for Raja 2025, as Bou Buttu Bhuta unravels a tale of suspense and horror like never before.‚Äã

Going for the legacy now f*** going viral
Naam banaa brand aisa maange indian idol
Ghar lage church aur passport hai bible
Akela hua bore to revive kiye rival
Maybach hai gaadi maybach hai eyewear
Drip hai sophisticated instincts hain tribal
Pange saare offline payment hai cyber
Khaana peena clean poora body maare fibre
V twin w mein leta kabhi L nai
Ghadi hai mechanical dale isme cell nai
Phone rehta silent pe baje kabhi bell nai
You think youre a devil abhi dekha tune hell nai
Hell naw  tod tere bhai ka nai
Tere baap ka kasoor hai teri maai ka nai
Zamaana raha ye bhalaai ka nai
Mera vazan kam hua meri likhai ka nai
Bitch doobmaro
Badboy Og old school jaise umbro
Launde saare gaanon pe naache jaise bumbro
If you still hate on me f*** you bro
Turn your fun into funeral
Rap tera juvenile, mooh tera urinal
Kabhi rm 005 fm
Kabhi Cartier santons green dial arabic numerals
Mind chale jaise laga isme chip bro
Dedhsau ka crib bro dhai ki hai drip bro
Ye to iceberg ki tip bro
Teri nayka hai meri teri kart kari flip bro
Main abhi bhi hun ill bro abhi bhi hun sick bro teri leke mile kick bro
Kutte ki tarah bhaunk mat likh bro
Koodta phire tu you can jump on my d*** bro

Hotel lobby bani moshpit, travel hua falcon badboy in the cockpit
Pilot bhi bole o shit, take off bina license true story no shit
Wi fi make sure kare dealein saari sire chadhein
Verse likhun tight itni opps saare dheele pade
Patek phillipe boy heere usme neele jade
Kuch jal ke kaale hue kuch hater neele pade
Hath margeilla jacket ki jebon mein
Pair labelon ke ceo ke desk par
School ke baad kabhi fail ni hua launda
Dekh number kitne aate mujhe test kar
Sath bandiyan jo race unki guess kar
Bar mein liquor hain jo age unki guess kar
They allready know badboy hai best par
Sab khelein jab tak badboy hai rest par
Meri verses mein mera lifestyle hai
Relate bhi ni kar paoge
Gruebel forsey tourbillion cardan
calibrate bhi nai kar paoge
Teri jeet se zaada baatein haar ki meri
Celebrate bhi ni kar paaoge
Badboy ab kya laayega
Anticipate bhi ni kar paoge
